---
title: "Student AI Q&A Flow - BoneVisQA"
---

flowchart TD
    %% Colors
    classDef student fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:2px
    classDef system fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#388E3C,stroke-width:2px
    classDef ai fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#F9A825,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#FFECB3,stroke:#FF8F00,stroke-width:2px

    %% Start
    START((Start)) --> LOGIN

    %% Authentication
    LOGIN[🔐 Login to BoneVisQA]:::student
    LOGIN --> AUTH[Authenticate User]:::system
    AUTH --> DASHBOARD[Load Dashboard]:::system

    %% Navigate to AI Q&A
    DASHBOARD --> NAV[Navigate to AI Q&A]:::student
    NAV --> LOADCHAT[Load AI Chat Interface]:::system
    LOADCHAT --> HISTORY{Has Chat History?}:::decision
    HISTORY -->|Yes| LOADHIST[Load Previous Conversations]:::system
    HISTORY -->|No| NEWCHAT
    LOADHIST --> SELECT_CONV{Continue or New?}:::decision
    SELECT_CONV -->|Continue| RESTORE[Restore Conversation]:::system
    SELECT_CONV -->|New| NEWCHAT
    RESTORE --> DISPLAY_HIST[Display Chat History]:::system
    DISPLAY_HIST --> INPUT

    %% New Chat Session
    NEWCHAT[Start New Conversation]:::student
    NEWCHAT --> INPUT

    %% Input Phase
    INPUT[📝 Type Question]:::student
    INPUT --> ATTACH{Attach Image?}:::decision
    ATTACH -->|Yes| UPLOAD[📷 Upload/Select Bone Image]:::student
    ATTACH -->|No| PREVIEW
    UPLOAD --> VALIDATE[Validate Image]:::system
    VALIDATE --> PREVIEW[Preview Message]:::system

    %% Send Message
    PREVIEW --> SEND[Click Send]:::student
    SEND --> PROCESS[Process Request]:::system
    PROCESS --> AI_ANALYZE[🤖 AI Analyzes Question]:::ai
    AI_ANALYZE --> AI_CONTEXT[🤖 AI Checks Context & History]:::ai
    AI_CONTEXT --> AI_GENERATE[🤖 AI Generates Response]:::ai
    AI_GENERATE --> FORMAT[Format Response]:::system
    FORMAT --> DISPLAY[Display AI Response]:::system

    %% Review Response
    DISPLAY --> READ[📖 Read AI Response]:::student
    READ --> ACTION{Student Action?}:::decision

    %% Follow-up Options
    ACTION -->|Ask Follow-up| INPUT
    ACTION -->|Rate Response| RATE[⭐ Rate Response]:::student
    ACTION -->|View References| VIEWREF[View Cited References]:::student
    ACTION -->|End Chat| ENDCHAT

    RATE --> SAVE_RATE[Save Rating]:::system
    SAVE_RATE --> ACTION2{Continue?}:::decision
    ACTION2 -->|Yes| INPUT
    ACTION2 -->|No| ENDCHAT

    VIEWREF --> BROWSE[Browse Reference Material]:::student
    BROWSE --> ACTION3{Continue?}:::decision
    ACTION3 -->|Yes| INPUT
    ACTION3 -->|No| ENDCHAT

    %% End Chat
    ENDCHAT[End Conversation]:::student
    ENDCHAT --> SAVE_CONV[Save Conversation History]:::system
    SAVE_CONV --> RETURN[Return to Dashboard]:::student
    RETURN --> ENDNODE((End))
